title: Rep. Garamendi on Impeachment & Wildfires
itunes:title: Rep. Garamendi on Impeachment & Wildfires
description:
Kevin spoke with Matt Brooks, Republican strategist and Executive Director of the Republican Jewish Coalition, and Antjuan Seawright, Democratic Strategist, Founder and CEO of Blueprint Strategy and Former Senior Advisor to Hillary Clinton in SC. They discussed the impeachment inquiry, trade, and the killing of Abu Bakr Al-Baghdadi.

Kevin also spoke with Congressman John Garamendi of California about the wild fires and blackouts, including the impeachment inquiry.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
